    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Oh, why was He there as the Bearer of sin,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "If on Jesus thy guilt was not laid?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Oh, why from His side flowed the sin-cleansing blood,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "If His dying thy debt has not paid?"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Look! look! look and live!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "There is life for a look at the Crucified One,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "There is life at this moment for thee."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "It is not thy tears of repentance or prayers,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "But the blood, that redeemeth the soul;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "On Him, then, who shed it, thou mayest at once"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Thy weight of iniquities roll."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
